                <span style="color:var(--green)">90&ndash;100</span> &mdash; exact title or phrase match<br>
                <span style="color:var(--accent)">60&ndash;89</span> &mdash; strong content match<br>
                <span style="color:var(--muted)">below 60</span> &mdash; fuzzy / partial match<br><br>
